Today J dives into the musical world of HUNTR/X and KPop Demon Hunters to break down the hidden mythology, real-world K-Pop inspirations, and ancient Korean lore that might reveal the identity of the missing Hunter. From Rumi’s White Tiger symbolism 🐅 to Zoe’s Dragon motifs 🐉 and Mara’s Tortoise armor 🐢 — there’s one Guardian left unaccounted for… the Vermilion Bird of the South. 🔥

Could this missing Phoenix represent a new girl yet to debut? Or maybe someone we already know..
